timeline.bodyText:
😱 the previous implementation of the rule was complex and not using the MethodMatchers API.
we should use a matcher like:
  private static final MethodMatchers PRINT_STACK_TRACE_MATCHER = MethodMatchers.create()
    .ofSubTypes("java.lang.Throwable").names("printStackTrace").addWithoutParametersMatcher().build();

them checkMethodInvocation will become far more easier to read:
  private void checkMethodInvocation(MethodInvocationTree tree) {
    if (PRINT_STACK_TRACE_MATCHER.matches(tree)) {
      reportIssue(ExpressionUtils.methodName(tree), MESSAGE);
    }
  }

